n</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C3%B9-m%C3%A2u-1/poem-xk7xxanHaMU6GdkrLCNcwQ">Thù mâu 1 - 綢繆 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C3%B9-m%C3%A2u-2/poem-E6I60UeM0-4byK795u_ljQ">Thù mâu 2 - 綢繆 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-poKMVsKTu5nOsOOtpFmCOA">Tương quân - 湘君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Xi-hi%C3%AAu-2/poem-yvqzqyTo3OKRYdjAxZOKtw">Xi hiêu 2 - 鴟鴞2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
